"ogimage":"http://s3-media4.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/IRgz7vBT-llUheh9rYlu9g/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.0",
"reviewcomment":"Hands-down, the BEST maternity and nursing wear store in New York. Why? Selection - it is clear that the owner is careful and knowledgeable in her purchasing, as there is a good selection of all the better products out there for maternity and nursing wear. They stay true to their slogan of &#34;give up wine, coffee and sushi, but not fashion!&#34; They have such a great selection that I am always left with a stack of clothes that I actually really WANT to purchase, rather than - ugh, that&#39;ll do. Which is a wonderful way to feel during pregnancy, when you are rapidly expanding and feeling less than chic. The brand selection is extensive and different from other stores and Destination Maternity. Definitely head here is you want some other options than the somewhat plainer offerings from H&amp;M and Gap maternity (nothing wrong with either of these - they are great for extending the wardrobe a bit less expensively). Yes, they stock the some of the more expensive maternity lines, but if you purchase carefully you can use most of the items for entire maternity period, including breastfeeding. Some of the dresses I have from here are so nice I will definitely want to continue wearing after that. Also, with the higher price point comes better quality items, so they are all holding up nicely to lots of washing an wearing.<br><br>All the staff are extremely helpful, always offering their opinions and styling advice. I love going to this store - I just have to save up a bit before I go!",
